  "title": "Sales & Team Growth Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are expanding our sales organization and looking for driven individuals who want to grow into leadership roles. This position offers structured training, mentorship, and hands-on exposure to team management.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Execute daily sales activities and client engagement</p></li><li><p>Learn leadership fundamentals through coaching and shadowing</p></li><li><p>Support onboarding and training of new team members</p></li><li><p>Participate in leadership development workshops</p></li><li><p>Build strong professional relationships with clients and teammates</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong communication and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and target driven</p></li><li><p>Open to feedback and continuous improvement</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You Gain:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Clear promotion pathway into leadership</p></li><li><p>Structured training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Performance-based rewards and recognition</p></li><li><p>Supportive, growth-driven culture</p></li></ul>",
